# Phase 18 Implementation Plan: The Tactile Sovereign Simulator

**Directive:** V18 Management Conversation вЂ” EU4-Style Windows, Colorful Ideology Grid, Satellite Map
**Cross-Reference:** [docs/UI_PRINCIPLES.md](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/docs/UI_PRINCIPLES.md), [implementation_plan_phase17.md](file:///C:/Users/zephy/.gemini/antigravity/brain/d82755e2-b20b-4e4e-88a9-a419e6646b6d/implementation_plan_phase17.md)

---

## Background

The current UI is a fixed CSS grid dashboard. Phase 18 transforms it into a spatial, windowed command center with:
- Draggable/resizable "Sovereign Windows" (EU4-style)
- A colorful 11Г—11 ideology grid with fullscreen mode and filter bar  
- Country profile popout window
- Satellite world map (zoomable with react-leaflet)
- UI Principles documentation codifying the Glass Cockpit / Perception Gap design language

---

## Proposed Changes

### Step 1 вЂ” Install `react-rnd`

```powershell
cd ui && npm install react-rnd --legacy-peer-deps
```

`react-rnd` provides drag + resize out of the box. No need for `@dnd-kit` overhead.

---

### Step 2 вЂ” Window Manager Foundation

#### [NEW] [WindowManager.tsx](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/ui/src/context/WindowManager.tsx)

`WindowManagerContext` вЂ” tracks open/closed state, z-index (focus order), and maximized state for each window. IDs: [ideology](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/brinkmanship_engine/tests/journey_tests.rs#305-321), `worldMap`, `country`, `telemetry`, `intel`, `demographics`.

Key functions: `openWindow(id)`, `closeWindow(id)`, `bringToFront(id)`, `toggleMaximize(id)`. Positions stored in `localStorage`.

#### [NEW] [SovereignWindow.tsx](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/ui/src/components/SovereignWindow.tsx)

The `<SovereignWindow>` wrapper using `react-rnd`. Props:
```typescript
interface SovereignWindowProps {
  id: string;
  title: string;
  defaultPosition: { x: number; y: number };
  defaultSize: { width: number; height: number };
  children: React.ReactNode;
  onClose?: () => void;
  canMaximize?: boolean;
}
```
Features: drag handle (title bar), close вњ•, maximize в¤ў, minimize _, amber border glow on focus, CRT scanline header, framer-motion `AnimatePresence` mount/unmount.

---

### Step 3 вЂ” IdeologyGrid Component

#### [NEW] [IdeologyGrid.tsx](file:///c:/Users/zephy/Documents/Brinkmanship/ui/src/app/components/IdeologyGrid.tsx)

The 11Г—11 colorful political matrix. Color formula (per `UI_PRINCIPLES.md В§III`):
```
dist = в€љ(xВІ + yВІ)
saturation = clamp((dist / 7.07) Г— 100, 0, 100)
hue = quadrant_base (Blue/Red/Green/Yellow per quadrant)
cell = hsl(hue, saturation%, 38%)
```

Props: `currentPos`, `perceivedPos`, `positionHistory`, `flavorLabel`, `onCellHover` (shows label tooltip from engine's 121-cell lookup).

**Filter Bar** (bottom of component, shown in fullscreen):

| Icon | Filter | Action |
|:-----|:-------|:-------|
| рџ—єпёЏ Grid | Overlay 121 labels | Toggle text labels on cells |
| рџ”Ґ Heatmap | Faction lean overlay | Darken cells by faction dominance |
| рџЊЉ Trajectory | Comet trail | Show `positionHistory` dots |
| рџ‘ЃпёЏ Veil | Perception overlay | Show perceived vs. real gap |

**Fullscreen behavior:** clicking the expand icon dispatches `pause_simulation` to the backend (`POST /api/pause`), then expands to a `fixed inset-0 z-[1000]` overlay.

